snippet.title: Baltic Folk - Official Announcement Trailer | OTK Games Expo 2024
snippet.description:
Baltic Folk is a magical tavern simulation game developed by SneakyBox. Players will embody a young innkeeper helping your witch grandmother manage, decorate, and expand their cozy traveling tavern. Baltic Folk is coming soon to PC (Steam).
